  25 Jun 2006; Alin Nastac <mrness@gentoo.org> libbtctl-0.6.0-r1.ebuild:
  Stable on x86 (#122262).

*libbtctl-0.6.0-r1 (22 Apr 2006)

  22 Apr 2006; Alin Nastac <mrness@gentoo.org>
  -files/libbtctl-0.4.1-enable_python.patch,
  +files/libbtctl-0.6.0-aclocal_openobex.patch,
  +files/libbtctl-0.6.0-libdir.patch, +libbtctl-0.6.0-r1.ebuild:
  Fix configure error when build against >=dev-libs/openobex-1.1.

  17 Feb 2006; Michael Hanselmann <hansmi@gentoo.org> libbtctl-0.5.0.ebuild:
  Stable on ppc.

  09 Feb 2006; Alastair Tse <liquidx@gentoo.org> libbtctl-0.4.1.ebuild,
  libbtctl-0.4.1-r1.ebuild, libbtctl-0.5.0.ebuild, libbtctl-0.6.0.ebuild:
  change openobex dependency atom (#122262)

*libbtctl-0.6.0 (07 Feb 2006)

